edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars

Class DQEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars.DQEntry

  • public class DQEntry
extends Object
    This class represents an entry in DistanceQueue. It's main purpose is just to associate a star with its distance from a given point.
